name: Introduction to Screen Printing
description:
Are you interested in learning about screen printing but not sure where to start? This class is will give you an overview of the process, some basic skills to get you started, and a chance to try your hand at printing your own shirt. It covers:

  • basic theory
  • equipment and tools used
  • basics of preparing artwork for print
Walk out with a shirt you've printed! Several classes are being scheduled for weekdays and weekends at the end of January and in mid February, 2014. You will be notified of available dates in January. Places are filling up quickly, don't wait until they're all taken! 6 places per class 1.5 hours A great gift for the crafty and/or creatively inclined!!

name: Intermediate Screen Printing
description:
Do you now the basics of screen printing and are ready to learn more? You can bring in your own (1 colour) shirt design and put some new screen printing skills under your belt. This class will cover:
  • coating screens
  • two colour print set up
  • start to finish screen printing process
  • brief Photoshop tutorial
Several classes are being scheduled for weekdays and weekends at the end of January and in mid February, 2014. You will be notified of available dates in January. Places are filling up quickly, don't wait until they're all taken! Prerequisite: Introduction to Screen Printing Class 4 places per class 2 hours A great gift for the crafty and/or creatively inclined!!
